<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= pageTitle %> | MyTaxCalcs</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Use the free payroll tax calculator to estimate federal withholding, Social Security tax, Medicare tax, state withholding, and net paycheck amount.">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/favicon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5193834725888549" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/>
            <rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span>MyTaxCalcs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
        <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">States</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="/calculators">All Calculators</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="calc-hero">
    <div class="calc-hero-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Paycheck Tax Estimator</div>
      <h1>Payroll Tax Calculator</h1>
      <p>Estimate paycheck withholding, FICA taxes, optional state withholding, and take-home pay.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="calc-main">
    <div class="calc-layout">
      <section class="calc-form-card">
        <div class="calc-form-header">
          <div class="calc-form-icon" style="background:#fff1f2; color:#e11d48;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Paycheck Information</h2>
        </div>
        <form method="POST" action="/payroll-tax-calculator" class="calc-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Gross Pay Per Paycheck</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="grossPay" value="<%= form.grossPay || '' %>" placeholder="2,500.00" step="0.01" required></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Pay Frequency</label>
            <select name="payFrequency">
              <option value="weekly" <%= form.payFrequency === "weekly" ? "selected" : "" %>>Weekly</option>
              <option value="biweekly" <%= !form.payFrequency || form.payFrequency === "biweekly" ? "selected" : "" %>>Biweekly</option>
              <option value="semimonthly" <%= form.payFrequency === "semimonthly" ? "selected" : "" %>>Semi-monthly</option>
              <option value="monthly" <%= form.payFrequency === "monthly" ? "selected" : "" %>>Monthly</option>
              <option value="annual" <%= form.payFrequency === "annual" ? "selected" : "" %>>Annual</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Filing Status</label>
            <select name="filingStatus">
              <option value="single" <%= form.filingStatus === "single" ? "selected" : "" %>>Single</option>
              <option value="marriedJoint" <%= form.filingStatus === "marriedJoint" ? "selected" : "" %>>Married Filing Jointly</option>
              <option value="marriedSeparate" <%= form.filingStatus === "marriedSeparate" ? "selected" : "" %>>Married Filing Separately</option>
              <option value="headHousehold" <%= form.filingStatus === "headHousehold" ? "selected" : "" %>>Head of Household</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Pre-Tax Deductions Per Paycheck</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="preTaxDeductions" value="<%= form.preTaxDeductions || '' %>" placeholder="200.00" step="0.01"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Post-Tax Deductions Per Paycheck</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="postTaxDeductions" value="<%= form.postTaxDeductions || '' %>" placeholder="0.00" step="0.01"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Extra Federal Withholding Per Paycheck</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="federalExtraWithholding" value="<%= form.federalExtraWithholding || '' %>" placeholder="0.00" step="0.01"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>State Withholding Rate (%)</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">%</span>
            <input type="number" name="stateTaxRate" value="<%= form.stateTaxRate || '' %>" placeholder="5.0" step="0.001"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Year-to-Date Wages Before This Paycheck</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><span class="input-prefix">$</span>
            <input type="number" name="ytdWagesBeforeThisPaycheck" value="<%= form.ytdWagesBeforeThisPaycheck || '' %>" placeholder="0.00" step="0.01"></div>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="calc-submit-btn">Calculate Payroll Taxes <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section class="calc-results-card">
        <div class="calc-form-header">
          <div class="calc-form-icon" style="background:#fff1f2; color:#e11d48;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Estimated Results</h2>
        </div>
        <% if (!result) { %>
          <div class="results-empty">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v16"/></svg>
            <p>Enter paycheck details to estimate payroll taxes and net pay.</p>
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="results-grid">
            <div class="result-row"><span>Tax Year</span><strong><%= result.taxYear %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Gross Pay</span><strong>$<%= result.grossPay.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Taxable Pay Estimate</span><strong>$<%= result.taxablePay.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Federal Withholding Est.</span><strong>$<%= result.estimatedFederalWithholding.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Social Security Tax</span><strong>$<%= result.socialSecurityTax.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Medicare Tax</span><strong>$<%= result.medicareTax.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Additional Medicare Tax</span><strong>$<%= result.additionalMedicareTax.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>State Withholding Est.</span><strong>$<%= result.stateWithholding.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Total Tax Estimate</span><strong>$<%= result.totalTaxes.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Post-Tax Deductions</span><strong>$<%= result.postTaxDeductions.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
            <div class="result-row result-highlight refund">
              <span>Estimated Net Pay</span>
              <strong>$<%= result.netPay.toFixed(2) %></strong>
            </div>
            <div class="result-row"><span>Est. Annual Net Pay</span><strong>$<%= result.estimatedAnnualNetPay.toFixed(2) %></strong></div>
          </div>
        <% } %>
        <div class="results-disclaimer">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          Estimate only. Actual withholding may vary based on Form W-4, benefits, state rules, local taxes, and employer settings.
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="calc-content-wrapper">
      <section class="content seo-content">
        <p class="eyebrow dark">Payroll Tax Guide</p>
        <h2>How this payroll tax calculator works</h2>
        <p>This payroll tax calculator estimates paycheck deductions by annualizing your gross pay, applying a simplified federal income tax estimate, calculating Social Security and Medicare taxes, and subtracting optional state withholding and post-tax deductions.</p>
        <div class="seo-grid">
          <div class="seo-mini-card"><h3>Federal withholding</h3><p>The federal withholding estimate is based on annualized taxable pay, filing status, the standard deduction, and federal tax brackets. It is not a full Form W-4 calculation.</p></div>
          <div class="seo-mini-card"><h3>FICA taxes</h3><p>FICA generally includes Social Security tax and Medicare tax. Social Security has an annual wage base limit, while Medicare tax does not.</p></div>
          <div class="seo-mini-card"><h3>Net paycheck</h3><p>Estimated net pay is calculated by subtracting pre-tax deductions, estimated taxes, and post-tax deductions from gross pay.</p></div>
        </div>
        <h2>Payroll tax FAQ</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>What taxes usually come out of a paycheck?</h3><p>Common paycheck deductions include federal income tax withholding, Social Security tax, Medicare tax, state income tax withholding, local taxes, benefits, retirement contributions, and other deductions.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>Is this the same as an official payroll withholding calculation?</h3><p>No. This calculator provides a simplified estimate. Actual payroll withholding may depend on your Form W-4, employer payroll system, pre-tax benefit rules, state rules, and local taxes.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>What is Social Security tax?</h3><p>Social Security tax is part of FICA payroll tax. Employees pay a percentage of covered wages up to the annual Social Security wage base.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>What is Medicare tax?</h3><p>Medicare tax is another part of FICA payroll tax. It generally applies to all covered wages, and higher wages may also be subject to Additional Medicare Tax withholding.</p></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><h3>Why is my actual paycheck different?</h3><p>Actual paycheck amounts may differ because of health insurance, retirement deductions, employer benefits, local taxes, W-4 settings, payroll rounding, bonuses, overtime, and other items.</p></div>
        </div>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      </section>
      <section class="content related-calculators">
        <p class="eyebrow dark">Related Calculators</p>
        <h2>More tax calculators</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a href="/income-tax-calculator">Income Tax Calculator</a>
          <a href="/tax-refund-calculator">Tax Refund Calculator</a>
          <a href="/self-employment-tax-calculator">Self-Employment Tax</a>
          <a href="/capital-gains-tax-calculator">Capital Gains Tax</a>
          <a href="/sales-tax-calculator">Sales Tax Calculator</a>
          <a href="/calculators">All Calculators</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="/" class="footer-logo"><span class="logo-mark"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/><rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/></svg></span>MyTaxCalcs</a>
          <p>Free tax calculators for income tax, refunds, self-employment tax, capital gains tax, sales tax, payroll tax, and state income tax estimates.</p>
